.SH "NAME"
.IX Header "NAME"
Tk::Font \- a class for finding X Fonts
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.PP
.Vb 1
\& use Tk::Font;
.Ve
.Vb 4
\& $font = $widget->Font(foundry => 'adobe',
\&                       family  => 'times',
\&                       point   => 120
\&                      );
.Ve
.Vb 1
\& $font = $widget->Font('*-courier-medium-r-normal-*-*');
.Ve
